            <p class="content-intro">
                Eventide XI features enhanced progression for Relic weapons with
                custom aftermaths and expanded job access.
            </p>

            <section id="relic" class="weapon-section">
                <h2>Relic Weapons</h2>
                <p>
                    Relics and their aftermath effects have been completely
                    overhauled and redesigned to increase their power and
                    usability. In era-accurate servers, it might take you over a
                    year to obtain a relic, but on <strong>Eventide</strong> we've
                    drastically reduced the amount of time needed to invest so that
                    players can finally enjoy seeing the fruits of their labour without
                    getting burned out. Dynamis can only be run once a week but hundos
                    can drop for individual participants at an average rate of 10â€“20
                    per run. Expect to get your relic weapon within three months or
                    so of regular Dynamis runs.
                </p>

                <h3>Power and Scaling</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        All relic weapon skills have identical and increased FTP <br>
                        <ul>
                            <li>1H: 3.75 / 4.25 / 4.5</li>
                            <li>2H: 2.75 / 3.25 / 3.5</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Relic WS should always outperform TP Bonus weapons using
                        non-relic WS.
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Job Expansions</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>BLU</strong> added to Relic Sword tree: Relic Sword,
                        Glyptic Sword, Dynamis Sword, Caliburn, Excalibur.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>PUP</strong> added to Relic Knuckles tree: Relic Knuckles,
                        Militant Knuckles, Dynamis Knuckles, Caestus, Spharai.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>COR</strong> added to Relic Gun tree: Relic Gun, Marksman
                        Gun, Dynamis Gun, Ferdinand, Annihilator.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>GEO</strong> added to Relic Club tree: Relic Maul,
                        Battering Maul, Dynamis Maul, Gullintani, Mjollnir
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Melee Relic Aftermaths</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Jobs affected:</strong> MNK, THF, DRK, WAR, BST, DRG,
                        SAM, NIN
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Effects:</strong> 5% Crit Hit Rate, 5 Subtle Blow
                        II, 5% Ability Haste, 5 Store TP, 5% Damage Reduction
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Duration:</strong> 120 seconds
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Specific Aftermath Changes</h3>
